{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2020-05-07-k8s-manage-context.markdown/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<!-- vim-markdown-toc Redcarpet -->\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\">前言</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#kubeconfig\">kubeconfig</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7\">工具</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#kconf\">kconf</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#kubectx-amp-amp-kubens\">kubectx&#x26;&#x26;kubens</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#kube-ps1\">kube-ps1</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#kubecolor\">kubecolor</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\">使用</a></li>\n</ul>\n<!-- vim-markdown-toc -->\n<h1 id=\"前言\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\" aria-label=\"前言 permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>前言</h1>\n<p>由于工作原因，需要操作多个 k8s 集群，所以整理下如何简单操作。</p>\n<h1 id=\"kubeconfig\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#kubeconfig\" aria-label=\"kubeconfig permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>kubeconfig</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/bd6640a8e003059ee98f84e7378d97f8337c5e0b/staging/src/k8s.io/client-go/tools/clientcmd/api/types.go#L31\">config</a>这个结构体定义了 kubeconfig 的所有配置，比较重要的字段有<code class=\"language-text\">Clusters,AuthInfos,Contexts</code>，\n在 clusters 和 authinfos 指定相关信息，然后通过 contexts 中的 Cluster 和 AuthInfo 字段来引用</p>\n<h1 id=\"工具\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7\" aria-label=\"工具 permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>工具</h1>\n<h2 id=\"kconf\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#kconf\" aria-label=\"kconf permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://github.com/particledecay/kconf\">kconf</a></h2>\n<p>kconf 用来添加 kubeconfig，</p>\n<p>使用方法：\n<code class=\"language-text\">kconf add /path/to/kubeconfig.conf --context-name=myContext</code></p>\n<p>也可以用来切换 context\n使用方法：\n<code class=\"language-text\">kconf use</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"kubectxkubens\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#kubectxkubens\" aria-label=\"kubectxkubens permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://github.com/ahmetb/kubectx\">kubectx&#x26;&#x26;kubens</a></h2>\n<p>kubectx 用来切换 context\n<img src=\"https://github.com/ahmetb/kubectx/raw/master/img/kubectx-demo.gif\" alt=\"使用情况\"></p>\n<p>kubens 用来切换 namespace\n<img src=\"https://github.com/ahmetb/kubectx/raw/master/img/kubens-demo.gif\" alt=\"使用情况\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"kube-ps1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#kube-ps1\" aria-label=\"kube ps1 permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://github.com/jonmosco/kube-ps1\">kube-ps1</a></h2>\n<p>kube-ps1 用来展示当前的 context 和 namespace\n<img src=\"https://github.com/jonmosco/kube-ps1/raw/master/img/kube-ps1.gif\" alt=\"kube-ps1\"></p>\n<p>kubeon 开启</p>\n<p>kubeoff -g 全局关闭</p>\n<h2 id=\"kubecolor\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#kubecolor\" aria-label=\"kubecolor permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://github.com/dty1er/kubecolor\">kubecolor</a></h2>\n<p>能让输出变得有颜色</p>\n<p>安装方法</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">brew install dty1er/tap/kubecolor</code></pre></div>\n<p>设置别名</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">alias kubectl=\"kubecolor\"</code></pre></div>\n<p><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/60682957/95733375-04929680-0cbd-11eb-82f3-adbcfecf4a3e.png\" alt=\"kubecolor\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"使用\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\" aria-label=\"使用 permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>使用</h1>\n<p>1、先把使用 kconf 添加配置</p>\n<p>2、然后使用 kconf 或者 kubectx 切换 context</p>\n<p>3、然后使用 kubens 切换 namespace</p>\n<p>4、然后使用 kubeon 打开命令行提示</p>\n<p>5、最后使用 kubeoff 关闭命令行提示</p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\">前言</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#kubeconfig\">kubeconfig</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7\">工具</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#kconf\">kconf</a></li>\n<li><a hr